data.description: New and Improved Price! Welcome to your dream home in the beautiful community of Ventura Village, a gated community that offers both security and tranquility. This Florida-style property is a true gem with its landscaped exterior and nature views. Step inside this stunning residence and be greeted by the high ceilings and archways, creating an open and spacious atmosphere throughout. The formal dining room and seating area offer an elegant space to entertain guests and create lasting memories. For those who love to work from home, the office space is flooded with natural light from the windows that overlook the front yard, providing a serene and inspiring environment. As you make your way to the heart of the home, you'll find the comfortable living room, perfect for relaxing and spending quality time with family. Adjacent to it, the large open kitchen is a chef's delight, equipped with modern amenities, an eating area, a bar with additional seating, and an island, all while offering views of the outdoors. The kitchen also boasts ample counter space, making it ideal for culinary enthusiasts and those who enjoy hosting gatherings. The primary bedroom is a true oasis, featuring large windows that provide breathtaking views of the surrounding nature, creating a peaceful and private retreat. The room also boasts two walk-in closets, offering plenty of storage space. Gleaming hardwood floors add a touch of sophistication to the room, continuing the elegant theme found throughout the house. The en suite bathroom is an absolute luxury with a soaking tub and a walk-in shower with glass doors, providing both relaxation and convenience. Double sinks and vanity space ensure that you have all the room you need to pamper yourself, while the tile flooring adds a touch of practicality. In addition to the primary suite, there are three more bedrooms, each adorned with hardwood floors and ceiling fans, offering comfort and style to all members of the household. Step out onto the screened back porch and be enchanted by the serene nature views that surround the property, providing a peaceful place to enjoy your morning coffee or host outdoor gatherings. With a 2-car garage, this home offers ample space for parking and storage, adding to the convenience and functionality of the home. The home also offers plantation shutters to offer elegance and style to the home. Don't miss the opportunity to call this captivating property your new home. Embrace the Florida lifestyle in the picturesque community of Ventura Village, where comfort, elegance, and natural beauty come together to create the perfect place to call home. ¤ Please see 3D Tour and Video ¤
